%N A396679 Expansion of e.g.f. -log(1 + W_2(-x)), where W_k(x) is the k-th iterate of LambertW(x).
%F A396679 a(n) = Sum_{k=1..n} n^(n-k) * binomial(n-1,k-1) * A001865(k).
%F A396679 a(n) = (n-1)! * Sum_{i,j,k >= 0 and i+j+k=n-1} n^i * (n-i)^j / (i!*j!).
%F A396679 a(n) ~ sqrt(Pi/2) * exp(exp(-1)*n) * n^(n - 1/2) * (1 - sqrt(2/((1 - exp(-1)) * Pi*n))/3). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Jun 29 2026
%o A396679 (PARI) my(N=20, x='x+O('x^N)); Vec(serlaplace(-log(1+lambertw(lambertw(-x)))))
